title: Grrr...
subTitle: Heartbroken and intoxicated, Rejimon stumbles into a lion's den at the zoo. Haridas, a guard, has to forcefully dive in to rescue him, earning media attention for the blunder.

title: China Town
subTitle: Mathukutty, Zachariah and Binoy, whose fathers were friends twenty years ago, return to Goa in order to reclaim a casino. But they face many challenges when a local goon tries to plot against them.

title: Irul
subTitle: Alex and Archana go on a trip but soon their car breaks down and they take shelter at a nearby house. However, things take a turn when the owner of the house behaves in a suspicious manner.

title: Kaththi
subTitle: A fugitive encounters his doppelganger and plots to steal his identity for a quick escape. However, fate intervenes as he chooses to embrace and fight for his look-alike's mission.

title: Chirikkum Thalika
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the best rib-tickling comedy scenes from various Malayalam movies featuring renowned actors and actresses.

title: Oru Indian Pranayakadha
subTitle: Aymanam Sidharthan, a leader of the youth wing of a local political party, hopes to succeed in politics. Irene, an Indo-Canadian woman making a documentary on Indian politics, is smitten with him.

title: Snehaveedu
subTitle: Ajayan comes back to his village to be with his ailing mother. However, things get strange when a boy comes to his house claiming to be his son.

title: Keshu Ee Veedinte Nadhan
subTitle: The life of an ordinary driver Keshu turns upside down when he wins a lottery worth 12 crores but his morality gets tested.

title: Natturajavu
subTitle: Pulikkattil, an affluent family man, is forced to bear the brunt and burden of his late father's unscrupulous past. Now, Karnan, a jail convict, decides to settle some old scores with him.

title: Thug Life
subTitle: Gang leader Sakthivel adopts Amaran after a gang war, but years later, a survival from assassination sparks doubt. Soon, Sakthivel suspects Amaran, igniting a conflict of loyalty and revenge.

title: Kannur Squad
subTitle: Determined to catch a notorious criminal, a police officer and his team undergoes several challenges as they scale the lengths of the country.

title: Kannur Squad
subTitle: Determined to catch a notorious criminal, a police officer and his team undergoes several challenges as they scale the lengths of the country.

title: Nagaravaridhi Naduvil Njan
subTitle: As Venu's dream is to secure an MBBS admission for his daughter, he decides to sell his property to get money for her education. However, his family members try to disrupt his plans.

title: Aanum Pennum
subTitle: An anthology of stories set in different timelines in history that explores female strength as the protagonists tackle the crises brought on by their male counterparts.

title: Ormayundo Ee Mukham
subTitle: Gautham is a young and successful businessman. His life dramatically changes when he meets Nithya, a girl who is suffering from short-term memory loss.

title: Action Hero Biju
subTitle: Biju Poulose leaves his teaching job to pursue his dream of serving in the police force. Posted as the sub-inspector in Cochin, he has to handle notorious criminals who indulge in unlawful activities.

title: Sagar Alias Jacky: Reloaded
subTitle: When her spouse, Manu, gets kidnapped, Indu approaches her confidante Sagar for succour. Soon, Sagar goes to Goa to save Manu and gets entangled in a lethal game.

title: Vettam
subTitle: Gopalakrishnan meets Veena while trying to smuggle a stolen necklace. Later, he accompanies Veena on her mission to unite with her lover.

title: Kantara
subTitle: When greed paves the way for betrayal, scheming and murder, a young tribal reluctantly dons the traditions of his ancestors to seek justice.

title: Bromance
subTitle: When Binto learns of his brother Shinto's disappearance, his search for Shinto leads him to collaborate with others, resulting in unforeseen turns, revelations, and memorable experiences.

title: In Ghost House Inn
subTitle: Thomas Kutty buys a haunted bungalow and convinces his friends to stay with him on the first night. The trouble begins when they actually see the ghost of the mistress who was killed 70 years ago.

title: In Ghost House Inn
subTitle: Thomas Kutty buys a haunted bungalow and convinces his friends to stay with him on the first night. The trouble begins when they actually see the ghost of the mistress who was killed 70 years ago.

title: Idukki Gold
subTitle: Michael returns to India and puts out an advertisement to try and find his old friends. Soon, he meets Ravi and Madan and together they set off on a road trip to meet the others.

title: Seelabathi
subTitle: Seelabhati along with her mother visits a remote village where she starts working as a computer teacher. When some students mysteriously disappear, the villagers start blaming her educational course.

title: Udayon
subTitle: Kunju is so obsessed with his land that he even grabs his sister's share by forging his father's will. Though he is known to be stubborn, his love for agriculture is appreciated by his youngest son.

title: Ananthabhadram
subTitle: To honour his mother's final wish, Ananthan attempts to light a lamp at the family temple. However, his quest is thwarted by an evil magician who seeks to harness the temple's hidden powers.

title: Minnal Murali
subTitle: Jaison, a young tailor, gains superpowers after being struck by lightning. However, he must thwart the evil intentions of an unexpected adversary to become the superhero that his rural village needs.

title: Hridayam
subTitle: Arun, a young man, enrols in an engineering college but falls prey to bad habits. As he grows up, he decides to turn over a new leaf and become a responsible adult.

title: Oru Maravathoor Kanavu
subTitle: Michael and his family buy a farm that is coveted by a rich man, who makes life difficult for him. Thereafter, Michael's brother, Chandy, comes to support him.

title: Two Countries
subTitle: Ullas schemes to marry Simran, woman with a disability, to avoid repaying a debt, but faces complications when Laya, a wealthy alcoholic, enters his life, turning his plans upside down.

title: Lollipop
subTitle: Franco, who runs an automobile workshop, and his sister Jenny, a college student, share a very strong bond. Matters take a turn when Franco falls in love with Jenny's enemy.
